data.title: 'I was made for bitcoin': Strategy CEO on his background
data.description: Strategy CEO Phong Le chats with Market Catalysts host Julie Hyman about what investors should know about the chief executive, touching upon his background and interests in the crypto space. Watch the full interview with Phong Le by clicking here. Also catch Yahoo Finance's full interview with Strategy co-founder and executive chairman Michael Saylor from our 2025 Invest conference. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.
